    base:desc "The Trajectory Generator Service computes optimal motion trajectories and publishes them via MQTT; the Control Application subscribes, translates the trajectory into motor command sequences and sends them to the Physical Crane Interface, which drives the motors and electromagnet. The Human‑Machine Interface can also issue commands through the same path."
