    base:desc "A C4‑style architecture where the Physical Crane Interface, Control Application, Logging Application, and Human‑Machine Interface run as Python processes on a PC; the digital twin services (Trajectory Generator, Simulation, Continuous Validation), MQTT broker, TimescaleDB, and Grafana run as Docker containers; communication occurs via MQTT messages and database reads/writes."
]

