    base:desc "Bidirectional communication uses MQTT (Eclipse Mosquitto) for command and event signalling, and TCP/IP connections to a TimescaleDB instance for time‑series data transfer; the Physical Crane Interface accesses motor controllers and sensors via a Python‑based serial/USB link to the Arduino."
]

instance dt_hosting_deployment : DTDFVocab:Deployment [
    base:desc "All components are hosted on a single personal computer; Docker containers host the database, MQTT broker, and Grafana dashboard, while the remaining services run as Python processes within the gantrylib package. Deployment is automated with a Docker‑compose file and the code is publicly available on GitHub."
]
